org.spongepowered.api.data.manipulator.mutable.entity

Interface SizeData

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataManipulator<SizeData,ImmutableSizeData>, DataSerializable, ValueContainer<SizeData>

    public interface SizeData
extends DataManipulator<SizeData,ImmutableSizeData>
    Represents the base and height sizes of an entity if it has physical form. Usually applies to all types of Entity.
